🌐 2. The Ecosystem War: Google vs. Apple vs. Microsoft

Situation: A non-tech-savvy relative wants a new phone, laptop, and smartwatch that just work together seamlessly.
Debate: Which ecosystem gives the best connected experience?

🟢 Team Google: “Affordable, cloud-synced, and flexible.”

⚪ Team Apple: “Smoothest integration and unmatched ecosystem.”

🔵 Team Microsoft: “Best productivity tools and cross-device support.”
